class="ui-heading3 title">
<a
href=#>Trump’s Blackwater Pardons Reveal Security Contractor Impunity Tendencies Typical for Republicans</a>
</strong><div
class=metadata><div
class=author>
<span>
<a
href=https://www.jurist.org/commentary/tag/author-iveta-cherneva class="url fn author-author-iveta-cherneva author-6450 post-author-link" rel=author>
<span
class=name> Iveta Cherneva</span>
</a>
